{"tid":1308764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有關人民鬥人民","createTime":"2019-07-12T03:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T03:08:14.000Z","uid":278881,"like":86,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"36c0d0679bd9e3852774aa133d41e17bba5f882f","tid":1308764,"uid":278881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:32:43.000Z","msg":"做左好多年cd rom去到今日覺得有必要開返個acc<br />\n最近好多有關人民鬥人民既post, 想特別討論返咩叫&quot;人民鬥人民&quot;<br />\n<br />\n首先, <span style=\"color: red;\">藍絲對黃絲並唔係人民鬥人民</span><br />\n呢個只係分化手段而唔係目的<br />\n藍絲跟本唔係我地既一部份, 而且更多本身都係政府中人, <span style=\"color: red;\">佢地並唔係人民既一部份</span><br />\n真正既人民鬥人民, 係黃藍之爭帶黎既<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武鬥和理非</span><br />\n<br />\n有睇呢幾日既post, 心水清應該會見到為左應唔應該反抗藍絲 / 守唔守牆, 開始有路線之爭互相指責<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢部份先係中共樂見</span><br />\n相反, 如果大家團結一致, 不論路線, 互相掩護咁反抗藍絲加政府<br />\n咁先係最有效, 因為只要大家有左身份認同, 有左敵我意識<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好快政府權力就會被架空<br />\n呢個先係不合作運動既精髓, 就係架空政府</span>"},{"pid":"1e5990999e57fcd98f6c9cfba1c33b905e5fd3ad","tid":1308764,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350d18b74ae84cf6ae558bb330d644a60cd0ee19","tid":1308764,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:35:33.000Z","msg":"全部同我入嚟記住勸交第一守則<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308521\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308521</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a23d05c31abe569a299d83987fa9abef622f114","tid":1308764,"uid":278881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2625cbf28cb8d075587373cd0d29e4eae5c199a0","tid":1308764,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:39:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56aa25692dedd1eb5ad0a41c929cf60862da0d4b","tid":1308764,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s